| `make clean` | Remove build artifacts |
| `cargo test` | Run Rust tests directly |

## Architecture

This project uses **Rust** with a library + binary pattern:

- **src/main.rs** — Binary entrypoint
- **src/lib.rs** — Library crate with shared logic
- **tests/integration_test.rs** — Integration tests

Key conventions:

- Library-first design (logic in lib.rs, thin main.rs)
- Unit tests in `src/lib.rs` via `#[cfg(test)]`
- Integration tests in `tests/` directory
- `cargo check` for fast compilation verification
- Uses stable Rust edition (2021)
